                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Caesari <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Aurelio Antoni<lb break="no" n="3"/>no <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> Septimi Severi <lb n="5"/>Pertinacis <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Parthici Adiabenici <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist heute verschollen. Die handschriftliche Überlieferung lautet: CAESARI/ MARCO ANTONI/NO AVG/P M SEVERI/ PERTINACIS AVG/ PARTICI ADIABENICI. Datierung: Ende 197 (Antonio Aug.), vor Jan. 198 (Annahme des Siegerbeinamens Parthicus maximus).</p>
            </div>
